ActCanada Transportation Act
SubjectBoating Safety Class Contribution Program
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2008-1014 of June 5, 2008; and (2) authorizing the Minister of Transport to enter into contribution agreements in an amount not to exceed $400,000 annually per recipient, for the purpose of implementing the BOATING SAFETY CLASS CONTRIBUTION PROGRAM.
